{"tid":2303901,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"「韓國新垣結衣」有多美？一張性感照讓日網友心服口服","createTime":"2020-11-28T10:16:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-28T11:30:58.000Z","uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8316b80ea3661e414e5e138c1fbb717ab16bb6a3","tid":2303901,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T10:16:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2020/11/26/realtime/9143663.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=1050&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2020%2F11%2F26%2Frealtime%2F9143663.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D1050%26exp%3D3600&h=b0c09a83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在日本土生土長的韓國女模Soyon，去年為時裝秀「關西Collection2019」走秀，知名度大漲，更有網友指出她外貌酷似日本女星新垣結衣，最近另有日本網友在「2ch」PO出她的火辣美照，並說「韓國的新垣結衣太可愛了」，讓網友也大讚「超越本尊了」、「根本不像，她更可愛」、「超越了新垣結衣，好不甘心啊」，但也有人一針見血地說：「你們只是著迷她的身材。」<br />\n<br />\nSoyon臉蛋清純可愛，卻有著魔鬼身材，也總是不吝惜秀出她33C、23、34的好身材，時常小露性感，或是扮成性感小野貓，引起日本網友喜愛，但近年日韓關係緊張，Soyon也收到一些日本網友的惡意回應，但她並不介意，表明依舊很喜歡日本，希望能在當地演藝圈努力開創屬於自己的一片天。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2020/11/26/realtime/9143664.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=1050&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2020%2F11%2F26%2Frealtime%2F9143664.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D1050%26exp%3D3600&h=00d51c97&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"26f44324b1c4a9978fc56b2a520f54c6aeacf819","tid":2303901,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T10:17:00.000Z","msg":"邊撚度似牙又<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ba9135b7b97c695001b0328efe592b155226a1d","tid":2303901,"uid":10290,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":